# Test Results Directory

This directory contains JSON output files from load testing and performance tests.

## Files

- `long_load_test_results_*.json` - Results from long-duration load tests run by `scripts/long_duration_load_test.py`

## Usage

Results are automatically saved here when running load tests. Files are named with timestamps for easy identification.

## Generated By

- `scripts/long_duration_load_test.py` - Long duration load testing script

## Note

Result JSON files are gitignored to avoid committing test data. Only this README is tracked.
